                Engineering Career Center
              
College of Engineering 


















The Engineering Career Center (ECC) provides helpful resources specifically geared toward UIC College of Engineering students and alumni for successfully securing internships, co-ops and jobs. We provide virtual and in-person career advising via scheduled appointments and drop-in advising.







            Engineering Career Center Hours
          Heading link



 
Copy link








            Drop-in hours for students during the Academic Year
          

            Monday - Friday, 10am-4pm (first come, first-served basis)
          



            Standard Business Hours
          

            Monday - Friday, 9am-5pm
          



            Drop-in Hours during Winter Break and Summer
          

            By Appointment Only
          





            (Excluding University Holidays)
          
















            Thanks to all who attended the Engineering & CS Job and Internship Fair!
          Heading link



 
Copy link



The Fall 2022 Engineering & Computer Science Job and Internship Fair took place on September 13 and 23, 2022. Thanks to all who attended!


      View Job Fair Information and Employer List
    















            Reserve our Interview Room!
          Heading link



 
Copy link



Have an interview and need a quiet space on campus? Students are now able to reserve our interview room in SEO 800! Our interview room space is available on a first-come, first-served basis. You must submit your request at least one full business day in advance. The room is only available during regular business hours, Monday – Friday, 9am – 4:30pm. It is best used for phone interviews, Skype, HireVue (or other types of recorded interviews), as well as technical coding interviews. The room contains a long table, chairs, and a large white board.
To reserve, complete this request form and a member of the career center team will reach out to confirm your request.
ALL students who use the interview room must abide by our interview room reservation policies.
 


      Request
    










            Online Resume Review Submission Form
          Heading link



 
Copy link



*Due to the Thanksgiving Holiday, we will not be accepting submissions from 11/23-11/27. We will re-open submissions on 11/28*
 
Students: Looking for an online resume review? Submit your resume below and our team will review your resume and provide direct feedback!
Please note this service is only available to current UIC Engineering students and UIC Engineering alumni three years post-graduation.
*Responses can take up to 2-3 business days*






